<article>
    <articleinfo>
        <title>DocBook parent POM usage guide</title>
    </articleinfo>
    <section>
        <title>Adding revision information to the document</title>
        <para>
            The POM version can be added automatically to the
            generated document by including the following in the <literal>&lt;bookinfo&gt;</literal>
            element:
        </para>
<programlisting><![CDATA[<releaseinfo>
    <?eval ${project.version}?>
</releaseinfo>]]></programlisting>
    </section>
</article>
